1
00:00:10,360 --> 00:00:11,760
What are you holding

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:12,920
in such a big box?

3
00:00:12,920 --> 00:00:14,850
This is a gift from my mom to Bai Qiu.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,200
To Bai Qiu.

5
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,920
It was deleted.

6
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,680
Qiongda.

7
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,360
Miss Bai.

8
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,079
Coffee.

9
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,480
Thanks, Uncle Li.

10
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,600
I accidentally fell asleep.

11
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:35,240
Take a break if you're tired.

12
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:51,960
Chao.

13
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,880
About last night,

14
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,120
I think I need to explain.

15
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,480
Although...

16
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,760
I'm not interested in you.

17
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,360
Stay away from me from now on.

18
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,440
Hello, seniors.

19
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:03,160
I'm Lin Yi'ang from the sports department.

20
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,360
A freshman this year.

21
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,680
We will be roommates from now on.

22
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,400
Please take care of me.

23
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,200
You're a freshman?

24
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,040
Well,

25
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,220
I just look a bit mature for my age.

26
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,400
Senior.

27
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,760
We've met before

28
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,240
at the swimming pool.

29
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,720
Do you remember me?

30
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:26,520
Xiaochao.

31
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,520
It's me, Xiaohao.

32
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,579
Do you remember me?

33
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,240
We used to be best friends.

34
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,040
I didn't expect to meet you here.

35
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:34,640
By the way,

36
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,040
I brought some local specialties from my hometown

37
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,370
to share with everyone.

38
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,640
Here, brother.

39
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:39,520
Senior.

40
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:42,320
Look.

41
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,560
Coconut candy.

42
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,360
Tamarind.

43
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,240
These were your favorites when you were a kid.

44
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,760
I just happened to bring them.

45
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,690
Thanks, junior.

46
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:50,840
Here, senior.

47
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,200
Pack your things quickly.

48
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:53,640
Immediately.

49
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,680
Right away.

50
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,720
He's our junior after all.

51
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,240
Be a little gentler to him.

52
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,400
By the way,

53
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,360
don't call me senior.

54
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,560
Just call me Wu Yu.

55
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,160
Okay.

56
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,420
Then I'll call you Brother Yu from now on.

57
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,400
Brother Yu.

58
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,960
Is this Li Weihao's bed?

59
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,440
By the way,

60
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,530
do you know about Li Weihao?

61
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,920
The teacher told me.

62
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,079
I'm not afraid of this.

63
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,880
I have strong masculine energy.

64
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,560
That's great.

65
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,360
Did you know

66
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,200
I've been feeling these past few days

67
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,560
that this room is chilly?

68
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,640
I reported it to the teacher.

69
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:28,040
No one dared to come over.

70
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,680
Senior.

71
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,560
Speaking of this,

72
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,960
I feel a little embarrassed.

73
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:33,600
What's wrong?

74
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,040
I don't have any bad habits,

75
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,760
except when I sleep,

76
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,000
I tend to snore.

77
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:41,400
I've been kicked out by many people before.

78
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,200
If you guys don't mind,

79
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,280
I'll stay here.

80
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,440
If you can't accept it,

81
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,280
just tell me,

82
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,400
and I'll leave right away.

83
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,360
No, no, no.

84
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,400
Snoring is good.

85
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,000
Now when I wake up in the middle of the night,

86
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,460
I just want to hear a sound.

87
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,960
That's great, Yu.

88
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:15,240
Lin Yi'ang.

89
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,080
Chao.

90
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,250
Chao, are you asleep? Chao.

91
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,440
Chao, come here.

92
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,680
Guess what I found.

93
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,840
There's a rooftop on our school building.

94
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,920
So?

95
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,000
Do you want to go up and take a look?

96
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,760
It's exactly like the one when we were kids.

97
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,560
No.

98
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,360
Lin Yi'ang.

99
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,880
Get up.

100
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,720
Your snoring kept me awake all night.

101
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,240
I'm sorry.

102
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,560
Sorry, Yu.

103
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,760
Here.

104
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:21,920
Sorry, Yu.

105
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,400
Sorry, Chao.

106
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,000
To express my apology,

107
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,520
how about this?

108
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:30,400
I'll bring breakfast for everyone later.

109
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,660
What do you want to eat?

110
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,720
Don't say that.

111
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:37,200
The last person who said that was

112
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,320
Li Weihao.

113
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,760
Then I won't bring it.

114
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:42,640
Let's go eat together.

115
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,560
Let's go.

116
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,290
Get dressed.

117
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,620
Chao, let's go.

118
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,120
You know what?

119
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,400
We've lived together for four years.

120
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:58,130
This is the first time he's had breakfast with us.

121
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,960
Then how does he usually eat?

122
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,640
Just by himself.

123
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,560
By himself?

124
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,090
Wouldn't he get depressed?

125
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,880
Don't.

126
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,440
The word "depression"

127
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:08,170
is a sensitive word in our dorm.

128
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,720
Yeah.

129
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,440
I heard Li Weihao had depression.

130
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,600
That's terrible.

131
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,400
I want this.

132
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,680
Give me a pancake.

133
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:27,760
[36 Years of Persistence]

134
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,760
Aren't there four people in our dorm?

135
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:30,800
I've seen you two.

136
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,880
What about the other one?

137
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:33,440
You mean Lin Jiaming?

138
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,840
I guess

139
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,760
he doesn't even dare to wander around the school.

140
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,480
Lin Jiaming.

141
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,539
Why does that name sound so familiar?

142
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:45,400
Isn't he the murderer in the school?

143
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,760
Keep your voice down.

144
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:50,240
No way.

145
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,280
They are in the same dorm?

146
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,400
Chao.

147
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,240
Yu.

148
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,880
So you two don't know the truth?

149
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,080
Are you Zhou Yi?

150
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:01,920
So gossipy.

151
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,560
Someone was killed.

152
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:05,520
Shouldn't I think about my own safety?

153
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,040
What's wrong with asking around?

154
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,680
What is their relationship anyway?

155
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,840
I don't know either.

156
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,560
But it is said that

157
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,920
Lin Jiaming moved into the dorm

158
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,120
because of Li Weihao.

159
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,720
Li Weihao is like his little nanny.

160
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,040
What are you looking at, Chao?

161
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:40,580
Chao, are you going to the guitar club recruitment?

162
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,080
What about elective courses?

163
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,880
What are you choosing next week?

164
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,920
If you have chosen your elective courses,

165
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,120
tell me,

166
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,180
we can go together.

167
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,520
Chao,

168
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,720
want to have dinner together tonight?

169
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,680
I'm reading.

170
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,360
Ming.

171
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,460
Ming, how is it?

172
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,120
Thanks, Ming.

173
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,680
Bye, Ming.

174
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,760
It's great to have money.

175
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,840
So,

176
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:32,100
they are in an employment relationship?

177
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,440
What employment?

178
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:36,420
Lin Jiaming didn't treat him like a human at all.

179
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:41,480
Ming,

180
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,200
here.

181
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:01,840
When was

182
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:03,280
this bought?

183
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:03,680
Just...

184
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,360
The ice has melted.

185
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,160
It's not fresh anymore.

186
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,920
I ask you, how do I eat it?

187
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,500
Are you hungry?

188
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,540
You are hungry.

189
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,760
You eat.

190
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,570
Open your mouth.

191
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,200
Is it good?

192
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,160
Good.

193
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,440
Not good.

194
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,120
Come on.

195
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,000
It's good, Ming.

196
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,160
Good, right? Good.

197
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:45,080
I can tell.

198
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,920
Because you're moved to tears.

199
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:48,720
Keep eating if it's good.

200
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,600
Eat more.

201
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:51,840
Have some more.

202
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,920
Eat up.

203
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:57,570
Thank you, Ming.

204
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,720
So delicious.

205
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,520
Hurry.

206
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,640
This is too much.

207
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:10,720
You can't bully people like this just because you have money.

208
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,640
No wonder they call him a murderer.

209
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:13,760
I tell you, whoever spent four years with him,

210
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:14,960
nobody could stand it.

211
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,090
Strictly speaking,

212
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,650
it's not four years.

213
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,130
They met when they were ten.

214
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:22,000
Met at ten?

215
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,200
Chao,

216
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,930
you've just been watching this for so many years?

217
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:32,920
Chao.

218
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,800
Lin Jiaming treats you like this,

219
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:36,200
why don't you fight back?

220
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,800
Putting these shoes online,

221
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:39,080
can sell for money, you know?

222
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,320
The pair he gave me last time,

223
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,400
guess how much I sold them for?

224
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,280
Over eight hundred.

225
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,540
Give them to me. Hurry.

226
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,880
He treats you like trash.

227
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,440
He plays with you, bullies you,

228
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,400
and treats you like a fool.

229
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,440
Can't you see that?

230
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,600
There are plenty of people in this world who treat me like a fool.

231
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,720
At least he gives me money.

232
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,320
He's quite generous.

233
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,850
Give them to me, I haven't finished brushing.

234
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,460
What do you need so much money for?

235
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:08,060
Do your parents deprive you of food or drink?

236
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,320
I have my uses.

237
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,360
These shoes,

238
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,400
there's a scratch.

239
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:21,460
Probably won't sell for a good price.

240
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,900
You really are like a dog kept by Lin Jiaming.

241
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,400
Wu Yu is right.

242
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,120
If a person

243
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,730
doesn't even want to call for help,

244
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:57,740
no one can save him.

245
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:07,600
No,

246
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,200
after saying all this,

247
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:11,920
is Lin Jiaming the murderer or not?

248
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:14,440
This question,

249
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:16,320
I'm afraid only Li Weihao knows.

250
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:37,760
What a beautiful smile.

251
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:43,680
Guixiang.

252
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:46,200
Guixiang.

253
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:57,760
Guixiang.

254
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,440
Weiguo, come and look.

255
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,800
Alright, stop looking.

256
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:11,840
Look at our family of three.

257
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:13,120
Stop looking.

258
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,400
Give it back.

259
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,200
What are you doing? Give it back.

260
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:18,920
Don't touch my son. Guixiang.

261
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:21,120
It's been over a week.

262
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:23,040
You haven't eaten or drunk.

263
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:25,920
What's the use of just staring at the photo album?

264
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:28,320
Yes, Xiaohao is gone.

265
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:31,040
We still have to look forward, right?

266
00:16:31,040 --> 00:16:32,770
We still have to live our lives.

267
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:39,480
Alright, alright.

268
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:42,600
How can I go on living?

269
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:45,320
Xiaohao is gone.

270
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,840
Mr. Chen said

271
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:50,440
Xiaohao had depression.

272
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,800
My son.

273
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,240
How could my son

274
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,160
get depression?

275
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:59,200
Okay, okay.

276
00:16:59,200 --> 00:16:59,640
Look at him. Okay, okay. Look at him.

277
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:01,080
Look how happy he is.

278
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:03,440
Look how happily he's smiling.

279
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,319
How could he have depression?

280
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:09,440
I don't understand.

281
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,839
I just don't understand.

282
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:14,079
Alright.

283
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:17,119
How could he get depression?

284
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:22,460
Alright, alright, Guixiang.

285
00:17:58,600 --> 00:17:59,800
You are so realistic.

286
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:00,760
Eat it.

287
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:01,760
That's enough.

288
00:18:01,760 --> 00:18:04,320
Eat here.

289
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,280
Here.

290
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,800
Young Master Lin, where are you?

291
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:15,760
None of your business.

292
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,240
I know you're in a bad mood.

293
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,560
I came to cheer you up.

294
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,560
I don't need it.

295
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:20,560
Are you crazy?

296
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,320
Keep running.

297
00:18:23,320 --> 00:18:24,000
Hey.

298
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:29,860
Can't you understand me? I don't need it.

299
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:32,120
Son, what are you doing?

300
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,120
Sorry, Mom.

301
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,920
Do you remember what day it is today?

302
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,440
I remember.

303
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,640
We only have a family dinner once a month.

304
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,200
And you don't even take it seriously.

305
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,240
Hurry up and get ready.

306
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,320
Dress smartly.

307
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:47,640
Okay, I got it.

308
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:04,200
I told you before to contact the board of directors of Qiongda.

309
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:06,060
Why hasn't there been a reply yet?

310
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:10,720
A student at Qiong University had an accident.

311
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:13,000
That kid is my driver's son.

312
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,560
Now the entire school board

313
00:19:14,560 --> 00:19:16,560
is busy dealing with the aftermath.

314
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:17,840
As for the school land,

315
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:19,240
it will just have to wait.

316
00:19:19,280 --> 00:19:20,640
It's just one person dead.

317
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:22,040
Is it really such a big deal?

318
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:23,520
The main thing is that this matter

319
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:25,050
involves Young Master Lin.

320
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,930
The school board is quite sensitive about it.

321
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,160
I see.

322
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,560
Honey,

323
00:19:57,560 --> 00:20:00,290
the kitchen made all your favorite dishes today.

324
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,520
Try some.

325
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,480
See how it tastes.

326
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:07,320
How is the school matter being handled?

327
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:09,400
Lisa Marie.

328
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:18,640
I've already asked Chaoyang to go to the TV station

329
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,240
and talk to the media.

330
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,900
It absolutely won't affect the company.

331
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,040
And?

332
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,080
Also,

333
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:28,360
regarding the public opinion about the school,

334
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:30,800
I want to wait for a new trending topic to appear,

335
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:32,960
then they naturally won't mention it anymore.

336
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:33,800
That's it?

337
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,200
And regarding the perpetrator,

338
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,800
I already have a target.

339
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:43,730
The same thing won't happen again.

340
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:46,960
Is this your plan?

341
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,400
What I want is not just from underwater to the surface,

342
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,760
but above the water.

343
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,800
Jiaming is still young.

344
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,480
You should give him some time.

345
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,080
Go.

346
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:01,680
Go to the study.

347
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,520
Think carefully.

348
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:05,560
Only come out

349
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:07,060
when you figure it out.

350
00:21:22,360 --> 00:21:23,640
Ten years ago,

351
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:24,760
at our construction site,

352
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,360
a worker died accidentally.

353
00:21:28,080 --> 00:21:31,560
At that time, our company was pushed into the teeth of the storm.

354
00:21:31,560 --> 00:21:32,920
You stepped forward

355
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:35,520
and established a migrant worker foundation,

356
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:38,020
which saved the company's image.

357
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,000
So I want to learn from you.

358
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,600
I want to use our group's name

359
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:44,000
to establish a

360
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:47,660
university student mental health foundation at the university.

361
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,360
That's more like it.

362
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,600
If the foundation has any issues

363
00:21:58,600 --> 00:21:59,960
that need help,

364
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,160
just ask Chaoyang.

365
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,600
I got it, Dad.

366
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:05,160
Let's eat.

367
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,360
Eat up.

368
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,600
The food is getting cold.

369
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:11,040
Come on, Jiaming, eat.

370
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:29,480
What are you doing here looking for me?

371
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,600
Does my son's matter

372
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:35,220
have anything to do with Lin Jiaming?

373
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:37,840
Given Young Master Lin's status,

374
00:22:37,840 --> 00:22:39,300
why would he kill your son?

375
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:43,520
What is this?

376
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:47,040
These are rumors.

377
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:47,920
Believe it or not,

378
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,760
in a few days,

379
00:22:48,760 --> 00:22:50,520
the public opinion will reverse.

380
00:22:50,520 --> 00:22:51,680
Did Lin Jiaming

381
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,640
really not do anything to wrong my son?

382
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:56,880
Mr. Li.

383
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:59,720
Weihao committed suicide.

384
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:02,080
The police have already made their conclusion.

385
00:23:02,080 --> 00:23:03,160
Right?

386
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,920
We have to face reality.

387
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:07,240
What's past is past.

388
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:08,320
We, the living,

389
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,480
must look forward.

390
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:12,320
Working hard for the Lins

391
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:14,080
is what we should do now.

392
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:15,560
I have to go.

393
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:17,040
A bunch of people are waiting for me inside.

394
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:17,640
By the way,

395
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,640
next time you come,

396
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,090
bring some 'candy'.

397
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:24,240
Zhu Xiaoyu.

398
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,320
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

399
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:35,440
I'm late.

400
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:36,760
It's fine.

401
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,000
Guess who I ran into today.

402
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:40,880
Who?

403
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,160
What handsome guy

404
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,760
could steal your heart away?

405
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,640
Am I that boy-crazy?

406
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,480
I ran into the

407
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,720
super influencer from your school,

408
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,720
Zhu Xiaoyu.

409
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:53,610
I don't know her.

410
00:24:54,120 --> 00:24:55,040
Just eat.

411
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:55,880
The food is getting cold.

412
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,040
You have no idea.

413
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,240
Lately,

414
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:59,600
any video she posts online

415
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:01,120
gets tens of thousands of likes.

416
00:25:01,120 --> 00:25:03,160
And the food she shares,

417
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,280
like molecular gastronomy

418
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:05,120
and chochin...

419
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:06,720
I've never even heard of them.

420
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:08,520
And those bags and jewelry she wears,

421
00:25:08,520 --> 00:25:09,880
just one of them

422
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,940
is worth several months of my salary.

423
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,200
Let me tell you,

424
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,400
those are all just a bluff.

425
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:15,800
Nothing to be envious of.

426
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:17,440
Molecular gastronomy

427
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:19,040
isn't even as tasty as jelly.

428
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:21,440
And those bucket bags

429
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,480
and shell bags

430
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:24,410
aren't as practical as a backpack.

431
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:27,360
Actually,

432
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:29,160
I'm not envious of those things.

433
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,840
I envy your

434
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:32,920
ability to live such a life.

435
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:35,400
When will I be like you?

436
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:53,640
Boss,

437
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,600
I ran out of my medicine.

438
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:56,800
Please prescribe me some more.

439
00:25:56,800 --> 00:25:59,000
How did you finish it so fast this time?

440
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:01,340
Has it gotten worse recently?

441
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:04,400
Before, it only hurt occasionally.

442
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:06,000
Now, it hurts almost every day.

443
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,880
Is it the stress of graduating,

444
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,880
or were you triggered by something?

445
00:26:10,560 --> 00:26:11,440
Just the usual.

446
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,380
Prescribe me another bottle.

447
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,400
Have you eaten, son?

448
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:48,700
Yes, I have.

449
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,440
It looks like a pharmacy behind you.

450
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,600
And you don't look so good.

451
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,280
I'm fine.

452
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:01,720
Anything else?

453
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,370
If not, I'll hang up.

454
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,320
No, wait.

455
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:07,760
A while ago, something happened to a student at your school.

456
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:08,960
Is that true?

457
00:27:13,320 --> 00:27:14,160
Yes.

458
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:17,280
Is this student named Li Weihao?

459
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,200
Yes.

460
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,320
Is it Xiaohao,

461
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:23,600
who used to live next door to us?

462
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:25,400
Yes.

463
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,200
See.

464
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:29,520
I told you it couldn't be a coincidence.

465
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:31,120
Back then,

466
00:27:31,120 --> 00:27:32,240
you and Xiaohao,

467
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,760
you two were so close.

468
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,920
His dad and I were out driving trucks,

469
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,780
away from home 200 days out of 300.

470
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,000
You were young,

471
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:41,280
even with money, you wouldn't buy anything good to eat.

472
00:27:41,280 --> 00:27:43,400
You just ate rice soaked in coconut milk.

473
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,680
Xiaohao treated you like a real brother.

474
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:46,760
Do you remember?

475
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:14,400
Xiaochao, come eat at my house.

476
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,260
My mom made coconut milk chicken.

477
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,600
Rice soaked in coconut milk.

478
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:27,840
Your favorite when you were a kid.

479
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:29,040
I just made it for you.

480
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,890
Take it away. I'm not eating it.

481
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:46,640
Chao.

482
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:51,810
I feel like you're different from when you were a kid.

483
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:52,850
You've changed.

484
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:59,840
Human cells are replaced every seven years.

485
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:02,100
We've been apart for eight years.

486
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,600
You can have friends,

487
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:05,560
but don't bother me.

488
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,440
Student.

489
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,280
It's your turn.

490
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:18,210
What do you want?

491
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:19,680
A portion of rice, ma'am.

492
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,640
No added flavors.

493
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:26,360
I promise.

494
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:28,600
What dishes do you want?

495
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,320
No dishes.

496
00:29:29,600 --> 00:29:31,330
Get me a bottle of coconut milk.

497
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,960
Do I really like eating this?

498
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:13,800
What are you eating?

499
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:15,120
It's so gross.

500
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,640
Are you broke at the end of the month?

501
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:19,040
Here.

502
00:30:19,360 --> 00:30:20,200
Eat mine.

503
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,840
Braised pork and bones in soy sauce.

504
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:24,960
Fried chicken chop.

505
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:25,680
Eat this first.

506
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:27,400
If it's not enough, I'll order more for you.

507
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,400
Thank you.

508
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,570
You're welcome.

509
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,680
What are you saying between brothers?

510
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:33,400
Come eat.

511
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:35,440
You're in the way. Move.

512
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,440
Step aside.

513
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:38,800
Boss.

514
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:41,920
While you were away these two days, that ghost came back.

515
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:42,960
Looks like our good roommate

516
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,760
has too much free time recently.

517
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:46,740
Are you still suspecting him?

518
00:30:49,800 --> 00:30:50,720
Let's go.

519
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:51,920
Let's go say hi.

520
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:05,160
Sorry.

521
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,080
My hand slipped.

522
00:31:06,080 --> 00:31:07,280
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

523
00:31:07,280 --> 00:31:09,320
The road is so wide, yet you had to walk here.

524
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:10,920
Are the two holes on your nose just for breathing?

525
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,600
You are so smart.

526
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:13,660
I did it on purpose.

527
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:15,320
What are you going to do,

528
00:31:15,320 --> 00:31:16,280
Yi'ang?

529
00:31:18,320 --> 00:31:19,120
Ignore him.

530
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:21,940
If a dog bites you, you don't bite it back.

531
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:24,760
To me,

532
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,240
you look more like a dog.

533
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:27,200
Say that again.

534
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,920
I can even say it twice.

535
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,840
Afu,

536
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:33,960
why are you so angry?

537
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,840
Isn't this how we used to play?

538
00:31:38,280 --> 00:31:39,200
I remember

539
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:41,160
we and Li Weihao

540
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:42,320
used to play like this.

541
00:31:42,320 --> 00:31:42,920
Yeah.

542
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:45,260
Right, Zhang Chao?

543
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:53,340
You have the nerve to mention Weihao?

544
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,840
You're more despicable than I thought.

545
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:57,640
Despicable?

546
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,400
I'm nowhere near

547
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,600
as despicable as you.

548
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:02,480
You just like playing dirty.

549
00:32:03,520 --> 00:32:04,400
Zhang Chao,

550
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,240
you're so sleazy.

551
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:08,280
But I don't like it.

552
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,160
Are you sick?

553
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:11,860
Still pretending?

554
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:13,120
Are you tired?

555
00:32:15,120 --> 00:32:17,320
Isn't this Lin Jiaming?

556
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,480
The murderer.

557
00:32:19,360 --> 00:32:20,800
Watch what you say.

558
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:23,760
I won't be soon.

559
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,880
Chao.

560
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:36,720
Watch.

561
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,120
A skinny guy and a fat guy.

562
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,040
Working hand in glove,

563
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,480
thick as thieves.

564
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:41,880
Chao.

565
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:43,960
Next time they mess with you,

566
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:44,880
just let me know.

567
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,640
I'll go straight up and smack them.

568
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,080
Listen to me.

569
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:48,680
I, Lin Yi'ang, don't have many other skills.

570
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,640
But my physique is enough to handle the two of them.

571
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:52,600
Provoking them won't do you any good.

572
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,600
Stay away from them.

573
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:54,600
Just ignore them.

574
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:56,800
Fine.

575
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,920
Wait, there's one thing I don't get.

576
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,640
Why are those two always targeting you?

577
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:07,720
Boss.

578
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,760
Setting up a foundation at this time,

579
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:09,920
is it a bit inappropriate?

580
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:10,720
Maybe we should wait a bit longer.

581
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:12,000
The thorn is already in.

582
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:12,880
At this point,

583
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,040
we have to pull it out by the roots.

584
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:14,840
Okay.

585
00:33:15,120 --> 00:33:16,650
If you've made up your mind,

586
00:33:16,760 --> 00:33:18,440
I will support you unconditionally.

587
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:19,120
What do you need me to do?

588
00:33:19,120 --> 00:33:20,120
You don't need to do anything.

589
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:22,120
Just keep an eye on Zhang Chao for me.

590
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:23,800
No problem.

591
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:25,860
I promise he won't cause any trouble.

592
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,480
As for the rest,

593
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,520
it's just me.

594
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:47,800
Lin Jiaming.

595
00:33:52,800 --> 00:33:53,600
Ms. Chen.

596
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:55,600
I was just looking for you too.

597
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:01,480
Looking for me?

598
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,680
Is it also about

599
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:05,600
the school graffiti wall?

600
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,880
Do you also think

601
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:09,719
I am the killer?

602
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:10,840
Of course not.

603
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:13,880
I don't want Weihao's incident

604
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:16,409
to cause another victim of malicious rumors.

605
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:17,960
I believe

606
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:20,600
what they say is not the real you.

607
00:34:22,120 --> 00:34:23,320
Thank you, Ms. Chen.

608
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:25,520
After all,

609
00:34:26,239 --> 00:34:28,500
Weihao and I grew up together as friends.

610
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,080
He had an accident.

611
00:34:31,719 --> 00:34:33,520
I couldn't accept it for a while.

612
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:35,800
I've been thinking these past few days

613
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,480
about what I can do for Weihao.

614
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:38,960
I decided

615
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,400
to use the Lin Group's name

616
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:44,320
to establish a mental health foundation.

617
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:46,239
A mental health foundation?

618
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:47,040
That's right.

619
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:50,520
First, it's to commemorate Weihao.

620
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:51,920
Second, it's to

621
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:54,679
let more college students like Weihao

622
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:56,400
get some help.

623
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,320
That's a good thing.

624
00:35:00,040 --> 00:35:01,080
I came here today

625
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:03,040
because I actually want to ask for your help.

626
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,240
How can I help you?

627
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:05,800
I'd like to invite you

628
00:35:07,160 --> 00:35:09,220
to be the advisor for our foundation.

629
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:10,440
Also,

630
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,120
to prove my innocence.

631
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,480
Then I must know,

632
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,800
between you and Weihao,

633
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,360
what exactly happened.

634
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:24,840
No problem.

635
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:26,280
Whatever you want to know,

636
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,000
just ask.

637
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:30,000
We'll try a different method today.

638
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:30,880
What method?

639
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:32,040
Hypnosis.

640
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:42,200
Why do you keep staring at me?

641
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:42,920
You,

642
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:45,560
Zhang Chao,

643
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:49,160
are the biggest problem.
